Datatrans
=========

This is a binding for the Datatrans library found at 
http://pilot.datatrans.biz/showcase/doc/iPhone_Library.zip


Building
========

Run `make` in the binding directory to build Datatrans.dll


Using Datatrans.dll with your own iOS App
======================================

Simply add Datatrans.dll to your project's References in MonoDevelop and you are
good to go!

Sample
======

The sample program in sample/.

Bugs
======

In the simulator only, when you type in some text that contains space 
(ie Firstname  Lastname in the credit card panel), the simulator crash.
The space trigger the iPhone text autocorrection that is buggy on the
simulator. Everything works well on device.

For more informations on this bug :
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/9357098/a-dialogviewcontroller-with-refreshrequested-and-entryelement-crash-when-text-en


